  "duaMeaning5": "uye udzikise bapiro rako mukuzvininipisa kwavari netsitsi uye uti, ‘Ishe, vanzwirei ngoni, sokundichengeta kwavakaita ndichiri muduku.",
  "duaMeaning6": "ngaakudzwe Mwari, iye anotonga zvirokwazvo. [Muporofita], usamhanyire kutaura zvakazarurwa zvisati zvakwana asi iti, ‘Ishe, ndiwedzerei muzivo!’",
